00:02:58,994 --> 00:03:00,075
but also encompasses a bit

70
00:03:00,115 --> 00:03:01,916
of the overall project pre-production.

71
00:03:03,429 --> 00:03:05,670
During the pre-production of Horizon Zero Dawn's quest,

72
00:03:05,751 --> 00:03:07,572
the entire company gathered into our canteen

73
00:03:07,592 --> 00:03:09,093
for a meeting we called Story Time

74
00:03:10,173 --> 00:03:11,154
with the narrative director.

75
00:03:11,714 --> 00:03:13,555
In this meeting, we were told the entire main story

76
00:03:13,575 --> 00:03:15,276
of Horizon Forbidden West in one go.

77
00:03:16,017 --> 00:03:17,918
Sometime after that meeting, I was assigned

78
00:03:17,958 --> 00:03:21,500
to create a section or a part of that overarching narrative

79
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:24,482
and that became known as the quest Death's Door.

80
00:03:26,048 --> 00:03:26,968
As part of that assignment,

81
