00:08:19,148 --> 00:08:20,869
And this is one of the first places where we wanted

200
00:08:20,889 --> 00:08:22,751
to explore how that gameplay would feel.

201
00:08:23,031 --> 00:08:24,452
And especially we wanted to do something

202
00:08:24,492 --> 00:08:25,532
with an interior space.

