00:23:30,603 --> 00:23:32,005
We're getting regular playtest feedback

548
00:23:32,025 --> 00:23:33,286
that informs our decision making.

549
00:23:33,747 --> 00:23:35,850
We're now at a level of certainty about the content

550
00:23:35,870 --> 00:23:37,432
that we're comfortable with other departments being.

