00:29:57,023 --> 00:29:59,865
So the effect of the art pass on the recluse chamber,

692
00:30:01,726 --> 00:30:03,247
that had some pretty big changes,

693
00:30:03,948 --> 00:30:05,249
and you'll see that in a second.

694
00:30:05,689 --> 00:30:06,510
I'm gonna show you a video.

695
00:30:07,310 --> 00:30:08,651
We got assistance from Core Design.

696
00:30:09,372 --> 00:30:10,192
That was really important,

697
00:30:10,212 --> 00:30:12,654
because we needed help with this giant spider thing,

698
00:30:12,674 --> 00:30:13,795
because it needed to be rigged,

699
00:30:13,855 --> 00:30:15,436
it needed to have complex scripting,

700
00:30:15,456 --> 00:30:16,477
it needed to have physics,

701
00:30:16,497 --> 00:30:17,578
it needed to have all kinds of stuff

702
00:30:17,598 --> 00:30:18,859
that we had no experience with.

703
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:21,701
This was probably the most complicated

704
00:30:21,741 --> 00:30:23,062
interactive object in the whole game.

705
00:30:24,799 --> 00:30:26,359
because people really thought of it like a machine

