00:31:40,074 --> 00:31:41,415
does pretty much the same stuff.

731
00:31:41,715 --> 00:31:42,856
Still has some ranged attacks,

732
00:31:43,456 --> 00:31:44,517
still tries to get up close to you.

733
00:31:49,728 --> 00:31:51,029
But now we have these weak points

734
00:31:51,049 --> 00:31:52,830
that are time dependent basically.

735
00:31:55,993 --> 00:31:58,775
So we also, like I said, did some experiments with the boss.

736
00:31:59,876 --> 00:32:00,997
The feedback on this version,

737
00:32:02,218 --> 00:32:03,900
players still never look at the boss.

738
00:32:05,021 --> 00:32:06,161
The weak points are too high.

739
00:32:06,262 --> 00:32:08,083
You have to push the camera up really high

740
00:32:08,103 --> 00:32:08,704
to see these things.

741
00:32:09,464 --> 00:32:10,505
The weak points are too simple.

742
00:32:12,607 --> 00:32:14,709
So we tried to fix this by doing some things.

743
00:32:14,789 --> 00:32:16,570
We tried to move the weak points down.

744
00:32:17,379 --> 00:32:20,522
We tried to change them to be either shoot or pull,

745
00:32:20,662 --> 00:32:21,543
but not both.

746
00:32:22,124 --> 00:32:24,046
We just kind of couldn't make up our mind

747
00:32:24,107 --> 00:32:25,428
whether we wanted to do pull or shoot

748
00:32:25,448 --> 00:32:27,010
because they both seem to have their merits.

749
00:32:27,130 --> 00:32:28,932
So we tried both for a while.

750
00:32:30,614 --> 00:32:32,036
And we added this new mechanic

751
00:32:32,056 --> 00:32:33,498
that I'll show you, the pulsing shield.

752
00:32:34,858 --> 00:32:38,499
So to try to tackle the idea that nobody looks at the boss,

753
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:40,801
I added this idea, we added this idea

754
00:32:40,881 --> 00:32:43,822
that when you shoot the boss, it would overload his shield

755
00:32:43,962 --> 00:32:46,123
and make this EMP pulse emanate out,

