00:32:46,363 --> 00:32:48,744
and that's what would expose the weak points.

757
00:32:49,524 --> 00:32:52,286
I really like this idea because it forced engagement

758
00:32:52,306 --> 00:32:54,667
with the boss, and it contextualized

759
00:32:55,067 --> 00:32:58,168
the weak points becoming exposed, as you see here.

