00:33:49,688 --> 00:33:52,530
that gave this sense of this kind of boiler room vibe.

780
00:33:52,931 --> 00:33:55,853
This end up in the ship product.

781
00:33:55,873 --> 00:33:56,894
This is pretty much how it looks.

782
00:33:58,977 --> 00:34:01,138
I wanted to tell the story of an older part of the facility

