00:34:03,760 --> 00:34:04,761
how we could deliver on that.

785
00:34:06,122 --> 00:34:09,104
So, during this period of iteration and parallel development

786
00:34:09,124 --> 00:34:11,145
we tried out new puzzle concepts,

787
00:34:11,946 --> 00:34:13,567
we integrated the first art passes,

