00:36:50,342 --> 00:36:51,783
Just beyond the security checkpoint,

854
00:36:51,823 --> 00:36:54,044
the player encounters a vast passage like a tunnel,

855
00:36:54,104 --> 00:36:56,545
roughly 100 meters long and 25 meters wide,

856
00:36:56,685 --> 00:36:58,086
ending with another gene lock door.

857
00:36:58,546 --> 00:37:01,347
This passage once featured a long suspended catwalk.

