1325
00:59:26,176 --> 00:59:26,577
Takeaways.

1326
00:59:28,198 --> 00:59:29,839
Have clarity on the story you're telling.

1327
00:59:30,613 --> 00:59:34,434
Though this quest changed a lot, the story we were telling remained relatively consistent

1328
00:59:34,634 --> 00:59:36,274
after the initial documentation phase.

1329
00:59:37,775 --> 00:59:42,676
Aim for your early designs to be representative and readable more so than beautiful or elegant

1330
00:59:42,816 --> 00:59:43,196
or fun.

1331
00:59:43,716 --> 00:59:45,536
This will save you both time and heartache.

1332
00:59:46,877 --> 00:59:51,398
When introducing or reintroducing a complex mechanic or concept, start with a small, easy

1333
00:59:51,438 --> 00:59:51,838
example.

1334
00:59:52,018 --> 00:59:53,358
Remember the idea of the nugget.

1335
00:59:55,054 --> 00:59:57,975
Be aware that when the larger design of the game shifts around your level

1336
00:59:58,395 --> 01:00:00,996
in a way that may require your level to accommodate those changes,

1337
01:00:01,296 --> 01:00:02,536
you have to embrace those changes.

1338
01:00:03,456 --> 01:00:06,677
In the game, we didn't have the shield wing as a thing that you got

1339
01:00:06,717 --> 01:00:08,238
as part of the main quest for a long time.

1340
01:00:08,278 --> 01:00:11,079
It was actually an optional piece of equipment you got in a side quest.

1341
01:00:11,839 --> 01:00:13,619
But once we actually moved it into the main quest,

1342
01:00:13,759 --> 01:00:16,880
we knew that we had to add it into this quest as a thing that you could use.

1343
01:00:18,808 --> 01:00:20,390
When tasked to explore big change,

1344
01:00:20,530 --> 01:00:22,553
make sure you understand the goals and limitations

1345
01:00:22,593 --> 01:00:23,795
defined by the gatekeeper,

1346
01:00:24,115 --> 01:00:26,599
and then sell those just as hard as the new idea.

1347
01:00:27,480 --> 01:00:28,982
If the people you're selling the idea to

1348
01:00:29,062 --> 01:00:31,085
understand the goals and limitations as well as you,

1349
01:00:31,425 --> 01:00:34,009
they'll know why your well-crafted idea

1350
01:00:34,129 --> 01:00:34,990
is the right solution.

1351
01:00:36,442 --> 01:00:38,745
And lastly, good ideas are like boomerangs.

1352
01:00:39,185 --> 01:00:41,628
Even when you throw them away, they often come back.

